Ing Pesus ning Pilipinas (Inglis: Philippine Peso) na ausan da namang '''piso''', ing opisyal a pera ning [[Filipinas|Pilipinas]].

Ing Philippine peso sign gagamitan ne ing simbulung "₱", na linto king pamanungkulan da ring [[Estados Unidos]] kapalit king oriyinal nang simbulu "$" na gagamitan da king Latin America.<ref name="₱">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dmNKAAAAMAAJ|title=A Guide Book of Philippine Paper Money|last=Shafer|first=Neil|publisher=[[Whitman Publishing]]|date=1964}}</ref> Ding aliwang simbulu ning pesus apin ding, "PHP", "PhP", "Php", o kaya "P" mu.

Ding perang papil ampong [[Barya|sisilyu]] ning Pilipinas manibat la king Security Plant Complex ning Sentrung Banku ning Pilipinas (Central Bank of the Philippines) king [[Lakanbaleng Quezon|Quezon City]].<ref>{{Cite web|title=Compare currencies in South East Asia|url=http://aroundtheworldinaday.com/philippines_thailand_comparison/thailand_currency_philippines_currency/}}</ref>

== Kasaysayan ==
Ing pesus menibat ya king pesus na ning [[Espanya|Kastila]] o Espanyol a pesus na detang da reng [[Manila galleons|galliun ning Menila]] manibat 1500 anggang 1800. King parewung pesus ampong doliyar menibatan la ring miyayaliwang pera king [[Latin America|Latinung Amerika]] ampo na king Estados Unidos, [[Hong Kong]]  ampo na ing Yuan da ring [[China|Intsik]] at Yen da ring [[Hapon|Apon]]. <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bsp.gov.ph/bspnotes/hist_curr.asp|title=Bangko Sentral ng Pilipinas – BSP Notes and Coins – History of Philippine Money}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Report of the Philippine commission to the President, January 31, 1900, page 142-149, Part IX: The Currency|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tn7hAAAAMAAJ&q=report+of+the+philippine+commission+january+1900+part+ix+currency&pg=PR7}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nationalinterest.org/feature/the-silver-way-explains-how-the-old-mexican-dollar-changed-20410|title='The Silver Way' Explains How the Old Mexican Dollar Changed the World}}</ref>

=== Bary bayu ding Espanyol ===
[[File:Manila_Mint_Museum,_PI_Piloncitos.jpg|alt=Piloncitos, a type of coin used by the pre-colonial peoples of the archipelago|thumb|Piloncitos, metung klasing sisilyu na ginamit bayu la dintang ding Espanyol.]]
Ding tribu kung nukarin ya ing Pilipinas ngeni makipag-barter la mu kanita karing kapara dang tribu. Ing e kasantingan ning barter, ginamit lang gintu ban pamalit -karing karelang kailangan king aldo-aldo da pablasang dakal gintu kanita king Pilipinas. Metung a klasing pera a ginamit da kanita ya ing Piloncitos, malating gintu na sasabyan dang pekamaluat o pekalumang pera king Pilipinas. 

=== Panaung Espanyol ===
[[File:Philip_V_Coin_silver,_8_Reales_Mexico.jpg|thumb|Pilak a columnario peso na menibat king Latin Amerika ning 1726-1770.]]
[[File:Doubloon.jpg|right|thumb|Espanyol a gintung onza o 8 escudos coin na menibat Latin Amerika na ating alagang 16 pilak a pesus.]]
[[File:PHL_-_50_centimos_alfonso_xii.jpg|thumb|Pilak a 50-sentimung sisilyu na megawa manibat 1864 anggang 1890s.]]
Ing pilak a pesus da ring Espanyol na ating alagang walung reales na mumunang pepakit da ring [[Fernando de Magallanes|Ekspedisyun ng Megallanes]] ning 1521 na megdalang marakalan ning 1595-ng pamaniyakup ng [[Miguel Lopez de Legazpi|Miguel Lopez de Legaspi]]. Ing pera daring tribu tinuluy pa mu naman kabang makasakup la karing Espanyol bilang toston o kapitnang-pesus a sisilyu. Ampo mu naman, Mepakit la naman ding Epanyul a gintung onza o walung-eskudung sisilyu na parwu baya na ning dolyar da ring Espanyol pero maka-alagang 16 a pilak a pesus.

Ding pekamaranun o pekalumang pilak a sisilyu na medala king panibatan da ring galleon a manibat [[Mehiku|Mexico]], maka-itsura lang macuquinas. Ding sisilyung a reni maralas lang atin [[Kristianismu|krus]] king arapan ampong ''coat-of-arms'' king kasumangid. Ding sisilyung areni mepalitan lang karing makinaryung-gawa a sisilyu na inaus dan [[Columnarios]] o "''dos mundos"'' ning 1732 na ating 27.07 gramu ning pilak.




=== Revolutionary Period ===
Ning mipaya kayari ning Pamanayag ning Kasarinlan ning Pilipinas kareng Espanyol ning [[Juniu 12]],1898 ing ''República Filipina'' (Republikang Pilipinu) king pamanunkulan ng [[Emilio Aguinaldo]], ginawa lang sariling perang papil ampong sisilyu na gagamit king ''likas-yaman'' na ning bansa. Ding mumunang pepalwal dang sisilyu inawus dong ''centavo'' na mamitna king pesus. Ing isla ning [[Isla ning Panay|Panay]] pepalwal ya namang barya. Kayari deng arakap ding Amerikanu i Aguinaldo king [[Palanan]], [[Isabela]], ing pesus pang-imagsikan mewala ya.

